11065020.text: At the entrance to the joint guard post, I found Won Han-seo and Jin-Rim, a member of the Pungbaekmun clan, who were in trouble. After hearing the story, Won Han-seo seemed to be dissatisfied with Suyang's betrayal of the trust of Pungbaek-mun in the past.

11065021.text: When I heard the story of Nok-Yun Chae, the head of the post, that Jin-Rim and Won Han-Seo went missing on their mission... It was also something I was worried about. Since the number of people at the check point is limited, the search for the missing person has to be limited.

11065022.text: When we arrived at the camp of the Black Dawn, the scenery there was terrible. The conditions of the prisoners we encountered there were not in a state that could answer anything.

11065023.text: Biryuha, who had always been positive, had a gloomy expression on her face. When I asked why she was worried about this, the source of Biryuha's concern was Pungbaekmun.

11065024.text: The members of the Pungbaek Mun, who were too reckless even if they were reckless, headed to the polluted crater deep in the headquarters of the Black Dawn to subdue the soulless.

11065025.text: I met So-hyang's father, Kwak-sa, whom I met in Soho Village, on Lake Bandal. It is said that Kwak-sa came to Haewol Continent after falling for the Black Dawn gang that said it could save the dead.

11065026.text: I got rid of the monsters and crossed the hill of the predator and arrived at the joint post. Every time I got rid of the monsters, Cheongwoon was excited and praised me.

11065027.text: When he arrived at the checkpoint, the friend he was looking for was not there.\nWhen I heard stories from the survivors, it seemed that a family who was supposed to be a friend's family had recently been kidnapped by the Black Dawn.

11065028.text: I found out that the refugee Je-jae, who was going to take revenge on his mother who died in the Black Dawn camp, was from the Black Dawn. Yeah... Maybe he was from the Black Dawn. But he did not have a mother who died at the hands of the Black Dawn.

11065029.text: I think he was planning to return to the Black Dawn by selling off the premise of the refuge. However, it seems that a merciless soulless man threw him into the crater.
